Class SyntaxElement

java.lang.Object
com.g63616e617a7a61.nonsensegenerator.model.SyntaxElement
public class SyntaxElement extends Object
Represents a syntax element with various linguistic properties and relationships. This class stores information about a word including its value, syntactic category, grammatical person, number, index position, and dependencies to other elements.
Author:
Tommaso Rovoletto
